{"tid":1191484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★$4000-部分已交表格的市民表示，職津處沒紀錄 要求重新填表","createTime":"2019-06-08T03:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T07:27:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2013b9fb5e7144198e983f81a5fd1bdb52d3129d","tid":1191484,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:13:47.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】政府向合資格人士派發4000元的關愛共享計劃，收到逾300萬份申請，但部分已交表格的市民表示，職津處沒他們的紀錄，要求他們重新填表，質疑政府遺失他們的資料。<br />\n<br />\n這裏是位於太子的在職家庭津貼辦事處，不少市民來查詢4000元計劃的申請進度，有部分人被通知要重新遞交申請表。<br />\n<br />\n到底表格去了哪裏？<br />\n<br />\n不願上鏡的廖先生向我地投訴，指早在三月投表入收集箱，及後一直收不到確認短訊，他多次向職津辦職員查詢，卻沒有正面回覆，質疑政府遺失他的資料。<br />\n<br />\n再填表之後又如何？廖先生表示職津處只是叫他等多幾個月，職津處強調沒有遺失申請表的紀錄，但沒解釋為何要求已交表的市民被要求重新填寫申請，只稱部份申請人沒收到確認通知，可能因為電話號碼或住址資料不詳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=350908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350908&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW89HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=3fb5e05f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350908&h=51da2108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=350908</a>"},{"pid":"75d202cbbeed3202a333a4dc80e0392764207280","tid":1191484,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c0c7211d16e358847921f773096e7975ece733","tid":1191484,"uid":145062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 咁搞派到2020都未派完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406849f0c9138cb039aed53aadbc83a5eec6fbbd","tid":1191484,"uid":237562,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"根本冇咁多錢比你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"